name: Alice in Wawaaaaland
description: I decided to create a bad trip alice. It’s simple. Yet it’s details. In he end. I just want to stare at it cause it’s super weird. And I love that. I love when I can see something so weird that I can’t help but want to stare at it. Perhaps something is so weird, it becomes attractive. I hope you all have a great day. Keep pushing that artwork. And be weird. Normal is boring. And again. What is normal?
